desc:
Main LZ: about 15mins walk to gondola;
LZ at gondola station: TRICKY -small, experienced pilots only!
ATTN: powr lines!  >> use main LZ

Toplanding also possible.
Large LZ with 2 windsocks, right beside road back to launch;
different bail-out LZ's

500m N of gondola station;
watch out for CABLES!!!
do NOT park here, but at gondola station.

Different LZ's for HG and PG:
- HG's land in the field to the North of the gondola station in 'Wasserauen';
- PG's: as indicated on map (to the south of railway station 'Wasserauen')

- 'Davos': info/ pictures to be found here: http://www.paraglidingearth.com/en-html/index.php?site=7883;
- 'Klosters': info/ pictures to be found here: http://www.paraglidingearth.com/en-html/index.php?site=7806;
- LZ 'Seewiese' (beside lake): CLOSED!

either:
